Question: Explain how to reach your home without using any street names
Answer:
The answer to this question really depends on where your starting position is, although I will assume you mean from Williamsburg. Regardless of the mode of transportation you choose, it would take a considerable amount of time to reach my.house. The ideal way is to take a plane which is about a 4 hour journey. Driving would probably take a week if you drove half the day for every day that week. You could also try taking a boat but that has considerable drawbacks considering my home is in a land-locked state.